  Requirements:
    php 5.2 or later
    GD2

  Summary:
    Pixidou is an open source AJAX image editor with basic features like:
    - adjust brightness
    - adjust contrast
    - cropping
    - flipping
    - negative 
    - resizing
    - rotating
    - tint

  Download:
    You can follow its evolution/contribute to the project at http://github.com/asvinb/pixidou/tree/master.

    Enjoy!
        Asvin Balloo